  <brief_title>Laparotomy Versus Percutaneous Puncture in Patients With Abdominal Compartment Syndrome During Acute Pancreatitis</brief_title>
  <acronym>DECOMPRESS</acronym>
  <official_title>Decompressive Laparotomy With Temporary Abdominal Closure Versus Percutaneous Puncture With Placement of Abdominal Catheter in Patients With Abdominal Compartment Syndrome During Acute Pancreatitis:Multicenter, Randomised, Controlled Study</official_title>
